## Ingestion Pipeline Details

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Drive as Google Drive
    participant Extract as Extract from File
    participant Split as RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter
    participant Embed as OpenAI Embeddings
    participant Pinecone as Pinecone Vector Store
    
    User->>Ingest_Trigger: Run Ingestion
    Ingest_Trigger->>Drive: Download Document
    Drive-->>Extract: File Content
    Extract-->>Split: Raw Text
    Split-->>Embed: Text Chunks (500-1000 tokens)
    Embed-->>Pinecone: Vectors + Metadata
    Pinecone-->>User: Upsert Complete
```

### Chunking Strategy
- **Splitter**: RecursiveCharacterTextSplitter
- **Chunk Size**: ~500-1000 tokens
- **Overlap**: 100-200 tokens for context preservation
- **Metadata**: Source file, page/section, timestamp

