## Query Flow (Voice RAG Agent)

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Webhook
    participant Agent as Voice RAG Agent
    participant Tool as VectorStoreTool
    participant Pinecone
    participant LLM as OpenAI Chat
    
    User->>Webhook: POST {question}
    Webhook->>Agent: Question
    Agent->>Tool: Search Query
    Tool->>Pinecone: Vector Search (top-k=5)
    Pinecone-->>Tool: Relevant Chunks
    Tool-->>Agent: Context
    Agent->>LLM: Question + Context
    LLM-->>Agent: Answer
    Agent-->>Webhook: JSON Response
    Webhook-->>User: Answer
```

